@startuml
title 미핏 - 한 면접 시나리오 시퀀스 (Setup → Session → Lambda → Report)

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #555555
  ActorBorderColor #2196F3
  LifeLineBorderColor #2196F3
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  ParticipantBorderColor #2196F3
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  ParticipantFontSize 11
  BoxBorderColor #B0BEC5
  BoxBackgroundColor #ECEFF1
}

actor "사용자" as U
participant "Frontend\n(React 19)" as FE
participant "Backend\n(Django 6)" as BE
database "PostgreSQL\n(RDS)" as DB
queue "Redis\n(Broker)" as Redis
participant "voice-api\n(FastAPI)" as VA
participant "S3\nvideo-files" as S3
participant "SNS / SQS\nFan-out" as MQ
participant "Lambda\n4 종" as Lambda
participant "interview-\nanalysis-report\nWorker" as Analyzer

== Step 1. Setup & Start ==

U -> FE : 면접 시작 클릭
FE -> BE : POST /interviews/interview-sessions/
activate BE
  BE -> DB : 티켓 검증 + 차감
  BE -> DB : InterviewSession 생성 (IN_PROGRESS)
  BE -> BE : GenerateInitialQuestionsService\n(LLM call gpt-4o-mini)
  BE --> FE : { uuid, first_question }
deactivate BE

FE -> FE : window.open(/interview/precheck/{uuid})

== Step 2. Precheck (3 단계) ==

FE -> FE : 카메라/마이크 + 브라우저/네트워크 + 음성 테스트

== Step 3. WebSocket Q&A 루프 ==

FE -> BE : WS connect /ws/interviews/{uuid}/
activate BE
BE -> BE : 티켓 인증 + 세션 검증
BE --> FE : { question }

FE -> VA : POST /api/v1/tts (Bearer)
activate VA
  VA --> FE : mp3 stream
deactivate VA

U <- FE : TTS 음성 재생

loop until no more questions
  U -> FE : 답변 (영상 + 음성)

  FE -> BE : POST /recordings/{uuid}/presign-part/
  BE --> FE : presigned URL

  FE -> S3 : PUT chunks (멀티파트)
  activate S3

  FE -> BE : POST /recordings/{uuid}/complete/
  BE -> S3 : complete multipart upload
  deactivate S3

  FE -> BE : WS submit_answer
  BE -> BE : SubmitAnswerService\n(FOLLOWUP: 후속 질문 / FULL_PROCESS: 다음)
  BE -> DB : InterviewTurn 저장
  BE --> FE : { next_question }
end

deactivate BE

U -> FE : "면접 종료"
FE -> BE : POST /interview-sessions/{uuid}/finish/
BE -> DB : status = COMPLETED + 스트릭 기록

== Step 4. AWS 영상 처리 파이프라인 (비동기) ==

S3 -> MQ : ObjectCreated event
activate MQ

MQ -> Lambda : SNS Fan-out → SQS
activate Lambda
  Lambda -> Lambda : video-converter (.mp4)
  Lambda -> Lambda : frame-extractor (.jpg)
  Lambda -> Lambda : audio-extractor (.wav + 16kHz)
  Lambda -> S3 : 결과 업로드
  Lambda -> MQ : SQS face-trigger\n(frame 추출 완료 시)
  MQ -> Lambda : face-analyzer 트리거\n(MediaPipe 1FPS 분석)
  Lambda -> S3 : face_analysis_result.json
deactivate Lambda

Lambda -> MQ : SQS step-complete (단계별)
deactivate MQ

MQ -> BE : kombu polling (sqs-celery-worker)
activate BE
  BE -> DB : InterviewRecording 업데이트
deactivate BE

== Step 5. 사용자 트리거 분석 리포트 ==

U -> FE : "분석 리포트 생성" 클릭
FE -> BE : POST /generate-report/
activate BE
  BE -> DB : 티켓 차감
  BE -> Redis : publish "analysis" 큐
deactivate BE

Redis -> Analyzer : pull task
activate Analyzer
  Analyzer -> DB : Load (Session + Turns + Resume + JD)
  Analyzer -> Lambda : voice-analyzer Lambda 병렬 호출
  Lambda --> Analyzer : 음성 지표 (속도/필러/침묵/음량)
  Analyzer -> Analyzer : LLMAnalyzer.analyze (5 카테고리)
  Analyzer -> DB : InterviewAnalysisReport (COMPLETED)
deactivate Analyzer

== Step 6. SSE 실시간 알림 ==

BE -> FE : SSE event (status=COMPLETED)
FE -> BE : GET /analysis-report/
BE --> FE : 5 카테고리 + 질문별 피드백 + 모범 답안

U <- FE : 리포트 화면 렌더링

footer MeFit - 한 면접의 전체 흐름 (REST + WebSocket + SSE + Event-driven)
@enduml
